xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 20, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cdk1701320618627.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cdk1701320618627.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cdk1701320618627.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cdk1701320618627\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A well-designed User Experience (UX) makes your customers want to use your application.\n\t\t\t<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Uniface UX</span> provides an out-of-the-box solution that enables you\n\t\tto modernize and enhance your application's user interface with ease. </p>\n<p class=\"p\">Uniface UX currently provides field, entity, and component level widgets to directly influence\n\t\t\tyour user experience.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Over the coming Uniface releases, Uniface UX is enhanced to include new constructs. You add\n\t\t\tthese constructs on top of your existing business model, allowing you to improve the\n\t\t\tuser experience while you continue to focus on your business model, data, rules, and the\n\t\t\tbusiness flow of your application.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The first Uniface UX deliverable is a set of field widgets called <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Uniface UX\n\t\t\t\tWidgets</span>. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cdk1701320618627__section_qjz_jq1_4cc\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cdk1701320618627__table_evy_ypg_q3c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Related learning videos</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"cdk1701320618627__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Title</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"cdk1701320618627__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">link</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"cdk1701320618627__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Uniface UX and UX Interface</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"cdk1701320618627__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/showcase/10552636/video/892169460\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Click to watch or listen Uniface UX and UX Interface video\" class=\"image\" id=\"cdk1701320618627__image_ish_yvv_q3c\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/My_Video_Button.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eeu1700028296908.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>UX Widget Interface</a><p>Web Widgets define the UX and UI of your web application. With UX Widget Interfaces you can implement your own UX Widgets, with layout constructs that match your preferred UI design.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tkx1725538389162.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Creating a UX Widget</a><p>To create a UX widget for a DSP field, an entity, or a component using the UX Widget Interface, you need to perform the following steps:</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qgj1701437193772.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>UX Widget States and API Functions</a><p>The following sections explain various UX widget states and it's API functions.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/erh1700028723550.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>UX Widget Troubleshooting Checklist</a><p>UX Widget Troubleshooting Checklist</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5441847\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5441847\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface UX Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 20, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 A well-designed User Experience (UX) makes your customers want to use your application. Uniface UX provides an out-of-the-box solution that enables you to modernize and enhance your application's user interface with ease. Uniface UX currently provides field, entity, and component level widgets to directly influence your user experience. Over the coming Uniface releases, Uniface UX is enhanced to include new constructs. You add these constructs on top of your existing business model, allowing you to improve the user experience while you continue to focus on your business model, data, rules, and the business flow of your application. The first Uniface UX deliverable is a set of field widgets called Uniface UX Widgets . Table 1. Related learning videos Title link Uniface UX and UX Interface Related Links UX Widget Interface Web Widgets define the UX and UI of your web application. With UX Widget Interfaces you can implement your own UX Widgets, with layout constructs that match your preferred UI design. Creating a UX Widget To create a UX widget for a DSP field, an entity, or a component using the UX Widget Interface, you need to perform the following steps: UX Widget States and API Functions The following sections explain various UX widget states and it's API functions. UX Widget Troubleshooting Checklist UX Widget Troubleshooting Checklist Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}